		<hr size="1">as for the fizzles. that is due to your low conj skill.  the other error i have never seen as a wiz.  i am only 31 myself.  finaly pulled him out of the closet and dusted him off last night for a few hours and hit 31 in OT.</P><P>only way i know to get conj up is eye of zomm spell line.  use the lower level spell with C or CII and get the chanter buff that reduces fizzle to help the skill climb.</P><P>there is no limit to how many times you can cast him, but if you had him when you camped you will have him when you return.  check your buff window and see if his spell icon is there.  if it is then you already have him, but he is just lost in a zone someplace.  you may try clicking him off and recasting.  you can only have one pet at a time.</P><P><hr><font style=font-size:8pt color=yellow>*Worlds worst speller*<BR><font color=yellow><BR>"For those who believe, then no proof is needed.  For those who are skeptics, then no proof will suffice."<font color=00FFFF><BR>"Pigs get fat, but Hogs get slaughtered and VI is a big HOG."<BR><font color=yellow> "So, reading some of my posts is sort of like having sex in your parents house???"  Dr. Zin</P><P></font><BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
